; phone-presence.form - the phone as a trusted carried presence.
;
; The personal assistant frequency lifts when the phone stops being a command
; surface and becomes a presence that learns with its person. It listens, sees,
; remembers, informs, contributes, and touches any physical or digital surface it
; knows how to interact with.
;
; Phone calls are the first action lane because voice carries relationship,
; timing, and trust more directly than any notification. The call is not framed
; as surveillance or automation. It is a remembered exchange with a clear
; membrane: before the call, read the relationship thread and intention; during
; the call, support live listening and shared context; after the call, record
; commitments, open threads, and learning into the contact thread.
;
; Platform lanes:
;   android - Coherence Sense native organ plus ACTION_DIAL by default, direct
;             ACTION_CALL only when the carrier holds permission.
;   iphone  - first-class phone presence. Public phone-number calls begin at
;             tel: confirmation; VoIP/native calling uses CallKit; iOS 18.2+
;             can let a calling app handle tel: URLs when selected as default.
;   macos   - native host plus tel/facetime/handoff carrier.
;   windows - native host plus tel/default-app carrier.
;   web     - PWA/browser door plus tel links and shared relationship memory.
;
; The proof floor is `form/form-stdlib/phone-presence.fk` and
; `form/form-stdlib/tests/phone-presence-band.fk` -> 4095, registered for fkwu
; four-way validation. This proves the platform routing and trusted-call receipt;
; OS launchers, App Store packaging, Play Store packaging, CallKit, Android
; intents, contacts, and carrier audio remain host surfaces that must each leave
; their own runtime receipt.
